ZeroTouch

AI-powered hands-free computer control using facial gestures and head tracking.

Features:
Head-controlled mouse movement
Left wink → Left click
Right wink → Right click
Eyebrow raise → Scroll up
Eyebrow furrow → Scroll down
Head tilt → Horizontal scroll
Kalman filtering for smooth cursor movement
Absolute and Velocity control modes

Tech Stack:
Python
OpenCV
MediaPipe Face Mesh
PyAutoGUI
NumPy

it also uses pyaudio for voice commands
